{"tid":2198742,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【武漢肺炎】法國單日增近 1 萬宗新確診　再創新高","createTime":"2020-09-11T14:38:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T15:24:15.000Z","uid":54337,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ccfc89e867ce0b614d646a4e82e9b2eeb17c9743","tid":2198742,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T14:38:05.000Z","msg":"【武漢肺炎】法國單日增近 1 萬宗新確診 再創新高<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E5%96%AE%E6%97%A5%E5%A2%9E%E8%BF%91-1-%E8%90%AC%E5%AE%97%E6%96%B0%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E5%86%8D%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2596%25AE%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A2%259E%25E8%25BF%2591-1-%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%25AE%2597%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA-%25E5%2586%258D%25E5%2589%25B5%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25AB%2598%2F&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3frnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=829902b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2596%25AE%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A2%259E%25E8%25BF%2591-1-%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%25AE%2597%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA-%25E5%2586%258D%25E5%2589%25B5%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25AB%2598%2F&h=4b152c2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E5%96%AE%E6%97%A5%E5%A2%9E%E8%BF%91-1-%E8%90%AC%E5%AE%97%E6%96%B0%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E5%86%8D%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98/</a>"},{"pid":"28660c02b5b6df27794d2e26758f7d47b44f4b25","tid":2198742,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T14:38:32.000Z","msg":"法國周四 (10/9) 單日新增武漢肺炎 (COVID-19) 確診個案再破紀錄，近一萬人在 24 小時內確診。<br />\n<br />\n法國衛生部門於首長級官員及衛生專家會議公佈最新單日確診數字，9,843 人確診感染，比早一日多近 900 人。截至香港時間今晨 (11/9) ，法國累計約 39.2 萬宗確診個案，逾 3 萬人死亡，死亡人數為全球第七多。入住深切治療部的患者近日也有增加趨勢，唯數字比 4 月高峰期低。<br />\n<br />\n法國科學委員會主席 Jean-Francois Delfraissy 提醒政府可能將要作出艱難決定控制疫情。政府也將在今日舉行會議，商討新抗疫政策，務求減慢病毒傳播。總統馬克龍表示，會議將讓公眾清楚了解到未來數周的計劃。他強調透明度極為重要，且需實事求是，不陷於任何形式的恐慌之中。<br />\n<br />\n世衛較早前就警告，歐洲疫情可能會再在 10&ndash;11 月重臨，不少國家也已重新封鎖部份疫情較嚴峻地區，以及提醒國民戴上口罩及保持社交距離。"},{"pid":"3017bf6b61403e826a2339856def325766795dd8","tid":2198742,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T14:38:52.000Z","msg":"成萬宗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9169d5d066e412f99de7ab7cc31c571f24df5b61","tid":2198742,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3017bf6b61403e826a2339856def325766795dd8","tid":2198742,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T14:38:52.000Z","msg":"成萬宗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T14:40:41.000Z","msg":"No one care<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0781bcadbb86c5449fae97007463375d09546815","tid":2198742,"uid":82938,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T14:43:22.000Z","msg":"麥巴比都中左<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以有排都唔駛開關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f2cfbec4b2fb3733f73af0c253f2293dbe9d5b2","tid":2198742,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T14:51:19.000Z","msg":"浪漫呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ff739366d24663d0e672f6d5f9